e explanation, before/after code fix, and a deep-dive mode powered by Claude Opus.\"\r\n  },\r\n  {\r\n    icon: \"вүЎЖ’Г„В»\", title: \"Adaptive Quizzes\", c: \"#fbbf24\", tag: \"3 MCQs в”¬в•– XP reward\",\r\n    desc: \"After each lesson, Veda generates 3 targeted multiple-choice questions. Correct answers unlock XP and advance your concept mastery percentage tracked in DynamoDB.\"\r\n  },\r\n  {\r\n    icon: \"вүЎЖ’ГҶВј\", title: \"AI Doubt Chat\", c: \"#10b981\", tag: \"Context-aware в”¬в•– streaming\",\r\n    desc: \"Ask anything about the code in the current file. Veda has full editor context О“ГҮГ¶ the active file, cursor line, and detected concepts О“ГҮГ¶ for genuinely relevant answers, not generic responses.\"\r\n  },\r\n  {\r\n    icon: \"вүЎЖ’ГҙГј\", title: \"GitHub Integration\", c: \"#f472b6\", tag: \"Octokit в”¬в•– any repo\",\r\n    desc: \"Browse and load any file from your GitHub repositories directly into the IDE. No git clone, no local setup О“ГҮГ¶ one click opens any file in the editor with full syntax highlighting.\"\r\n  },\r\n  {\r\n    icon: \"вүЎЖ’ГҙГӘ\", title: \"Skill Progression\", c: \"#06b6d4\", tag: \"DynamoDB в”¬в•– real-time\",\r\n    desc: \"Every mistake, lesson, and quiz answer is stored in DynamoDB with timestamps. Your mastery percentage per concept updates live as you interact, giving you a true learning trajectory.\"\r\n  },\r\n];\r\n\r\nconst STEPS = [\r\n  {\r\n    n: \"01\", icon: \"О“ВЈГ¬\", title: \"Write code naturally\",\r\n    desc: \"Work in the browser IDE exactly like VS Code. Open files from your GitHub repos or the built-in explorer. Veda stays out of your way until it has something genuinely useful to say.\"\r\n  },\r\n  {\r\n    n: \"02\", icon: \"О“ГңГӯ\", title: \"Veda detects the mistake\",\r\n    desc: \"After 30 seconds of inactivity, Claude Haiku scans your code via AWS Lambda. A confidence-gated classifier identifies the single most impactful concept to teach you right now.\"\r\n  },\r\n  {\r\n    n: \"03